title: PROJECT: event up now?? Yas activates effects.
body: I thought the project event was coming later in the patch, yet Yasuo's Project skin activates the effects. is this intentional?

replies.body: CAUGHT OUT WITH YOUR SCRIPTS GG RETARD
Mate are you OK? I think you're not getting enough sleep.

As far as I'm aware no specific dates were given for "Project: Sync" just "during patch 5.17 and 5.18", whereas the "Project: First Strike" was specified as the 8th of September through to the 15th of September, so it may be intentional.
